graph TD
    User[User / Terminal] -->|invokes| CLI[cli.py: argparse entry]
    CLI -->|parses args| Config[config.py: load settings]
    CLI -->|dispatches| Commands{Command router}
    Commands -->|fetch| Fetcher[fetcher.py: HTTP client]
    Commands -->|transform| Parser[parser.py: data cleanup]
    Commands -->|persist| Storage[storage.py: SQLite]
    Fetcher -->|JSON| Parser
    Parser --> Storage
    Storage -->|read| Reporter[reporter.py: render output]
    Reporter -->|stdout / file| User
